Middle of the Linked List -> Leetcode 876

Bruteforce approach:

public ListNode middleNode(ListNode head) {

        if (head == null || head.next == null) {
            return head;
        }

        ListNode temp = head;
        int count = 0;

        while (temp != null) {
            count++;
            temp = temp.next;
        }

        int mid = count / 2 + 1;
        temp = head;

        while (temp != null) {
            mid = mid - 1;

            if (mid == 0){
                break;
            }
            temp = temp.next;
        }

        return temp;
}
